&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Platform Architecture &amp;amp; Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the design, development, and deployment of core robotics platform software that underpins perception, planning, control, and fleet services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Systems Performance &amp;amp; Debugging:&lt;/strong&gt; Perform in-depth performance analysis and hardware/software debugging across Linux-based systems, ensuring reliability and real-time behavior.&lt;/li&gt;
